# Implementation Plan: DLHC Admin Panel

## Goal Description
Build the internal Super Admin Panel for the DLHC platform. While the User Dashboard is for companies generating letterheads, the Admin Panel is strictly for the Dovepeak platform administrators. It will be used to manage global system resources like Master Templates, User Accounts, Subscription Plans, and Platform Analytics.

The design will remain professional and data-dense, reusing the clean B2B SaaS components established during the User Dashboard phase.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]  
> Please review the proposed **Modules** below. Are there any specific admin capabilities you need for MVP that I haven't listed (e.g., manual billing overrides, support ticket viewer)? 
> 
